{"_response_info":{"status":"ok"},"id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/report-loan-shark.json","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/report-loan-shark","title":"Report a loan shark","format":"answer","updated_at":"2013-01-09T13:13:13+00:00","details":{"need_id":"936","business_proposition":false,"description":"Loan sharks are unlicensed moneylenders - if you use or spot one you can report them anonymously in a number of ways","language":"en","body":"\n<div class=\"summary\">\n<p>Loan sharks are illegal moneylenders who often charge very high interest rates - check if a company is licensed and how to report one that isn’t.</p>\n</div>\n\n<p>If you spot a loan shark, or have borrowed money from one, you can report them anonymously.</p>\n\n<h2>Report a loan shark</h2>\n\n<h3>In England</h3>\n\n<div class=\"contact\">\n<p><strong>Illegal Money Lending Team - England</strong><br />\n<a href=\"&#109;&#097;&#105;&#108;&#116;&#111;:&#114;&#101;&#112;&#111;&#114;&#116;&#097;&#108;&#111;&#097;&#110;&#115;&#104;&#097;&#114;&#107;&#064;&#115;&#116;&#111;&#112;&#108;&#111;&#097;&#110;&#115;&#104;&#097;&#114;&#107;&#115;&#046;&#103;&#111;&#118;&#046;&#117;&#107;\">&#114;&#101;&#112;&#111;&#114;&#116;&#097;&#108;&#111;&#097;&#110;&#115;&#104;&#097;&#114;&#107;&#064;&#115;&#116;&#111;&#112;&#108;&#111;&#097;&#110;&#115;&#104;&#097;&#114;&#107;&#115;&#046;&#103;&#111;&#118;&#046;&#117;&#107;</a><br />\n0300 555 2222<br />\nAvailable 24 hours <br />\nText LOAN SHARK and the lender’s details to 60003</p>\n</div>\n\n<h3>In Wales</h3>\n\n<div class=\"contact\">\n<p><strong>Wales Illegal Money Lending Unit</strong><br />\n<a href=\"&#109;&#097;&#105;&#108;&#116;&#111;:&#105;&#109;&#108;&#117;&#064;&#099;&#097;&#114;&#100;&#105;&#102;&#102;&#046;&#103;&#111;&#118;&#046;&#117;&#107;\">&#105;&#109;&#108;&#117;&#064;&#099;&#097;&#114;&#100;&#105;&#102;&#102;&#046;&#103;&#111;&#118;&#046;&#117;&#107;</a><br />\n0300 123 3311<br />\n24 hours<br />\nText LOAN SHARK and the lender’s details to 60003</p>\n</div>\n\n<h3>In Scotland</h3>\n\n<div class=\"contact\">\n<p><strong>Illegal Money Lending Team - Scotland</strong><br />\n<a href=\"&#109;&#097;&#105;&#108;&#116;&#111;:&#108;&#111;&#097;&#110;&#115;&#104;&#097;&#114;&#107;&#115;&#064;&#103;&#108;&#097;&#115;&#103;&#111;&#119;&#046;&#103;&#111;&#118;&#046;&#117;&#107;\">&#108;&#111;&#097;&#110;&#115;&#104;&#097;&#114;&#107;&#115;&#064;&#103;&#108;&#097;&#115;&#103;&#111;&#119;&#046;&#103;&#111;&#118;&#046;&#117;&#107;</a><br />\n0141 2876 655</p>\n</div>\n\n<h3>In Northern Ireland</h3>\n\n<div class=\"contact\">\n<p><strong>Trading Standards Consumerline - Northern Ireland</strong><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.consumerline.org/\" title=\"Trading Standards Consumerline website\" rel=\"external\">www.consumerline.org</a><br />\n0300 123 6262</p>\n</div>\n\n<h2>Check to see if a lender is licensed</h2>\n\n<p>You can check to see what companies have a licence.</p>\n\n<div class=\"contact\">\n<p><strong>Consumer Credit Register</strong>  <br />\n020 7211 8608<br />\nMonday to Friday 9:30am to 4pm    <br />\n<a href=\"http://www2.crw.gov.uk/pr/Default.aspx\" title=\"Check the Consumer Credit Register\" rel=\"external\">Consumer Credit Register</a></p>\n</div>\n\n","alternative_title":""},"tags":[{"title":"Court claims, debt and bankruptcy","id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/tags/tax%2Fcourt-claims-debt-bankruptcy.json","web_url":null,"details":{"description":"Includes recovering debts, registering for bankruptcy and as a creditor","short_description":null,"type":"section"},"content_with_tag":{"id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/with_tag.json?tag=tax%2Fcourt-claims-debt-bankruptcy","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/browse/tax/court-claims-debt-bankruptcy"},"parent":{"title":"Money and tax","id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/tags/tax.json","web_url":null,"details":{"description":"Includes VAT, debt and inheritance tax","short_description":null,"type":"section"},"content_with_tag":{"id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/with_tag.json?tag=tax","web_url":"https://